# ⚠️ S44 ANIMATION PROTECTIONS:
# The following 3 animations are FINAL from S44 — do not modify:
#   1. glass-input-pulse (4s ease-in-out infinite) — idle input glow
#   2. rainbow-glow-pulse (12s linear infinite) — CTA rainbow hue rotation
#   3. object-badge-dot-pulse (1.5s ease-in-out infinite) — badge scale
# Performance optimizations from S44 (will-change, containment, transform3d) MUST remain.
# New animations must ALSO have prefers-reduced-motion guards.
# New animations must COEXIST with S44 animations — no conflicts.
# Use DIFFERENT keyframe names (prefix with s45- if needed).

###############################################################################
# OBJECTIVE
###############################################################################
Add or refine subtle micro-animations that make the UI feel alive and modern.
No heavy animations. Every animation must respect prefers-reduced-motion.

###############################################################################
# ANIMATION PRINCIPLES
###############################################################################
principles:
  - Meaningful: animation communicates state change or relationship
  - Subtle: user shouldn't consciously notice it
  - Fast: 150-250ms for interactions, 300-500ms for transitions
  - Eased: cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1) for natural feel
  - No bounce/spring for a professional app (we're fleet tracking, not a game)
  - Always: prefers-reduced-motion → disable or reduce

###############################################################################
# IMPROVEMENTS TO CONSIDER
###############################################################################

### 1. Screen transitions
Current: instant switch between screens (no transition)
Improvement: subtle fade + slide (opacity 0→1 + translateY 8px→0)
Duration: 200ms
Where: MobileShell renderScreen()
prefers-reduced-motion: instant switch (current behavior)

### 2. Bottom sheet enter/exit
Current: appears instantly when isOpen changes
Improvement: slide up from bottom + fade overlay
Enter: translateY(100%) → translateY(0), 300ms
Exit: translateY(0) → translateY(100%), 200ms
Where: BottomSheet component (new from T7)
prefers-reduced-motion: instant

### 3. List item entrance (staggered)
Current: all items appear at once
Improvement: staggered fade-in (each item delays 30ms)
Duration: 200ms per item, max 10 items staggered
Where: objects-screen vehicle list
prefers-reduced-motion: no stagger

### 4. Button press feedback
Current: active:opacity-90 or active:bg-background/30
Improvement: add subtle scale: active:scale-[0.98] + transition
Duration: 100ms
Where: Button component (base class)
prefers-reduced-motion: keep (it's functional feedback)

### 5. Tab/segment switch
Current: instant color change with transition-colors
Improvement: add underline/background slide animation
Duration: 200ms
Where: SegmentedControl component (new from T7)
prefers-reduced-motion: instant

### 6. Bottom nav active indicator
Current: color change only
Improvement: add subtle indicator dot or underline slide
Duration: 200ms
Where: mobile-shell.tsx nav tabs
prefers-reduced-motion: instant color change

### 7. Glass container hover/focus
Current: hover:bg-background/50
Improvement: subtle scale + shadow increase on hover
Duration: 200ms
Where: glass CSS classes in index.css
prefers-reduced-motion: no scale, keep color change

###############################################################################
# DO NOT ADD
###############################################################################
anti-patterns:
  - ❌ Loading spinners with multiple colors
  - ❌ Continuous pulsing on non-focused elements (already have glass-input-pulse — enough)
  - ❌ Parallax or scroll-linked animations
  - ❌ 3D transforms
  - ❌ Sound effects
  - ❌ Confetti or particles
  - ❌ Animation duration > 500ms for interactions

###############################################################################
# EXECUTION ORDER
###############################################################################
order:
  1. Button press feedback (safest, tiny change)
  2. Bottom sheet enter/exit (visible improvement)
  3. Glass container interaction refinement
  4. Tab/segment animation
  5. Screen transitions (most impactful, test carefully)
  6. Bottom nav indicator
  7. List entrance (optional — only if time allows)

###############################################################################
# ACCEPTANCE CRITERIA
###############################################################################
verify:
  - [ ] All animations have prefers-reduced-motion guard
  - [ ] No animation > 500ms for interactions
  - [ ] 60fps on mobile (no jank)
  - [ ] Both themes work with animations
  - [ ] Animations feel professional, not playful
  - [ ] pnpm run build passes
  - [ ] CSS containment where needed
